      3 +----------+ 7          +----10----+
       /:         /|           /:         /|
      / :        / |          1 2        5 6
   1 +==========+5 |         +=====9====+  |
     # 2+ - - - # -+ 6       #  +- - 11-# -+
     # /        # /          0 3        4 7
     #/         #/           #/         #/
   0 +==========+ 4          +=====8=====+

z changes fastest, then y, then x.
